"{\"uid\": \"newsus.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-29-Team-Great-Britain-secures-historic-Olympic-bronze-in-women-s-diving-1vCAhTnqBLa-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Dan Williams  Copied  China\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s divers made a strong start, winning gold in the Women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Synchronized 3-meter Springboard. They finished ahead of a U.S. pair who took silver.  Australia had looked set to win bronze, only to make a mistake in their last dive, allowing the team from Great Britain to make it onto the podium instead. CGTN\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Dan Williams has the story.  For more, check out our exclusive content onCGTN Nowand subscribe to our weekly newsletter,The China Report.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"